&lt;p&gt;To use the Concrete Beam Calculator:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Reinforced Concrete Walls Sectional Analysis</title><link>https://BramSteensma.github.io/engineering/concrete_sections/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://BramSteensma.github.io/engineering/concrete_sections/</guid><description>&lt;h4 id="this-program-allows-accurate-analysis-of-sections-of-composite-walls-of-any-geometry-based-on-current-regulations-ds-60-the-following-are-determined"&gt;This program allows accurate analysis of sections of composite walls of any geometry, based on current regulations (DS 60). The following are determined:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3D interaction diagrams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reinforcement modification&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Displacement demand&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Moment-Curvature diagram&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confinement length&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

